latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I have always had trouble sleeping during my period. I have to sleep rigidly, set regular alarms, and I can't get a good night's sleep. But not anymore! 
I recently got this Whisper hamper with Whisper Bindazzz Nights and the Koala Soft pads!
The Bindazzz Nights pad is up to 75% longer & has a wider back which gives up to 0% leaks all night long! Isn’t that like dream come true? 
And the Koala Soft is up to 85% longer and has a super soft top sheet that allows me to sleep in any position during my period nights! 

The Whisper Nights pads have really helped me through my period nights, and I think you should try them as well💁🏻‍♀️

 #SleepBindazzz #Whisper #SanitaryPad #Menstruation #PeriodNights #BindazzzNights
